choices.text: You have woken up in a strange apartment, phones missing, and with little memory of the recent past. Which day is it Which year is it even After some searching, you establish today's date, because the calendar on the wall displays it. Also, you have found the remains of an old newspaper from 1 January in your handbag, which has that weekday printed on the front page. Help B rge and se figure out if today is Friday.
